      "title": "Introduction",
      "level": 1,
      "content": "According to Wikipedia:\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Installation",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "Install the gnutls package.\n\nFor integration with the Apache HTTP Server install mod_gnutls.\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Usage",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "See certtool(1) for the command used in the following sections and the info document for the API documentation.\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Generate a private key",
      "level": 3,
      "content": "```\n$ certtool --generate-privkey --outfile private_key\n```\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Generate a certificate signing request",
      "level": 3,
      "content": "```\n$ certtool --generate-request --load-privkey private_key --outfile file\n```\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Generate a self-signed certificate",
      "level": 3,
      "content": "```\n$ certtool --generate-self-signed --load-privkey private_key --outfile file\n```\n\n"
    },
    {
      "title": "Inspect a certificate",
      "level": 3,
      "content": "```\n$ certtool --certificate-info --infile file\n```\n\n"
    },
    {
